## Summary
Amplitude Activation is a self-serve personalization platform that enables 1:1 personalization through segmentation (cohorts and computations), personalization (predictions and recommendations), and delivery mechanisms (syncs and APIs) to drive 15-30% lift in conversions without requiring data scientists or engineers.

